title: He Knew He Was Right (2004) BBC TV
description:
Another Anthony Trollope BBC? TV mini-series. It's pretty good, but not nearly
as good as Trollope's longest "The Way We Live Now." Nor is it as good as "jane
Eyre 2006." Both of these better movies I intended to upload, but found thay
were already available. I strongly recommend readers to download both of them.
In my house they are big favorites.

More information on the enclosed video can be found in the enclosed text file.
